    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would be a great project or a budget-friendly daily driver for someone willing to put in a little work. The exterior shows its age with some noticeable scratches, a few small dings, and some fading on the clear coat. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and a small tear on the driver's seat, though all basic electronics remain functional. While the car starts and drives, it will likely need new tires and a brake service soon, and there is a slow oil leak that should be addressed. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that reflects its age and mileage, priced accordingly for its current state.",
