    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. This vehicle remains in pristine, showroom condition, featuring an unblemished exterior and a cabin that retains its original factory freshness. Meticulously inspected and fully documented, it offers a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast to acquire a vehicle of peerless quality and mechanical integrity.",
