      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade E92 M3, a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. This specimen features the S65 4.0L V8, delivering an 8,400 RPM redline through eight individual throttle bodies. Mechanically flawless, it boasts documented rod bearing and throttle actuator service, ensuring the long-term integrity of the high-revving valvetrain. The chassis remains razor-sharp with Electronic Damping Control (EDC) and a pristine M-variable differential lock. The paint depth is consistent across all panels, and the interior retains its factory-fresh matte finish with zero bolster wear. A turn-key collector piece for the true driving enthusiast.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Low mileage. Garage kept. Full service history. No accidents.",
      "price": 46000.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly museum-grade 2021 BMW M2 Competition in the iconic Long Beach Blue Metallic. This vehicle has been fastidiously kept in a climate-controlled garage and presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is absolutely flawless, having been treated with a multi-stage paint correction and protected by a full-body ceramic coating and front-end Paint Protection Film (PPF). There are zero rock chips, door dings, or swirl marks to be found. Inside, the Black Dakota leather with contrasting blue stitching remains firm and supple, with no visible bolster wear or creasing. The cabin retains its original new-car scent and has never been smoked in. Mechanically, the car is in peak condition, with a full service history documented exclusively through BMW authorized centers. It has never been tracked, modified, or driven in inclement weather. For the discerning collector or enthusiast seeking a pristine, untouched example of this driver-focused machine, this M2 is unparalleled. All keys, original window sticker, and service receipts are included.",
      "price": 47900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to the highest standards of automotive preservation. This unit exhibits pristine aesthetic qualities and mechanical integrity consistent with a showroom-floor specimen. Meticulously curated and virtually indistinguishable from new, it represents a rare opportunity for the discerning enthusiast seeking uncompromising quality and a peerless driving experience.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to show you this absolute gem. It\u2019s honestly in pristine condition\u2014it looks and drives just like it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve truly pampered this car, and it\u2019s basically like new both inside and out. If you\u2019ve been looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and kept in flawless shape, this is definitely the one for you. Come say hi and take a look, you\u2019re going to love it! \ud83d\ude0a",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 2005 BMW M3 (E46) in a rare, concours-ready configuration. This chassis is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system that pulls linearly to an 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-spec Variable M Differential Lock for optimal torque vectoring. Extensive mechanical preservation includes a reinforced rear subframe, VAC-treated rod bearings, and a comprehensive Beisan VANOS overhaul. The suspension geometry remains true to OEM specifications with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, ensuring the legendary 50/50 weight distribution is fully realized. This is a turn-key example with a pristine undercarriage and zero deferred maintenance, catering to the most discerning collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
